text: Gregory Bayne (born 10 March 1972) is a South African rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:South African male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Africa Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Johannesburg
